Description:
LOW MAINTENANCE HOME IN AN UNRIVALED LOCALE!
Ray White is proud to present this fantastic opportunity for all First home buyers, downsizers and astute investors looking to be nestled in a highly sought-after and super central pocket of Dandenong. This gorgeous home is ready for you to move into and also provides a highly convenient lifestyle as you're only walking distance to a plethora of local businesses and facilities.
Offering 2 very good-sized bedrooms with BIR, a spacious, sun-filled family area and dining/meals area which is adjacent to the delightful kitchen that's equipped with gas cooking and an abundance of cupboard space. The main bathroom, separate toilet and laundry make up the interior of this lovely home.
Features of this home include: ducted heating, private backyard, single lock up garage and much more.
It doesn't get more central than this! Walking distance to, Dandenong Market, Dandenong Plaza, Dandenong Hospital, Chisholm Institute, Multiple Pre-Schools, Primary Schools, High Schools, public transport, local shops and major arterial such as Princes Highway, Eastlink and Monash.
This gem will not last long with the location and features like these, we highly recommend you act soon before you see a SOLD sticker on the board!!
Call Ben Jusufi or Burak Gul for any further information!
*PHOTO I.D. REQUIRED UPON INSPECTION*

Description:
Immaculate and Low Maintenance
Whether you are a first home buyer, looking at downsizing or taking advantage of an investment, then this jam-packed unit is for you. With only a short distance to all amenities this home provides the ideal lifestyle that you have been looking for!
This freshly renovated cosy property offers two spacious robed bedrooms, a living/meals area which is adjacent to the well-appointed kitchen with electric stove top, dishwasher, stainless steel oven and an abundance of cupboard space.
Further features to this home includes split system, single garage and a spacious secured alfresco.
Located within a stone's throw away from Dandenong South Primary School, Dandenong High School, Dandenong Hospital, Dandenong CBD, Dandenong Bypass/Eastlink and recreational facilities. With a bus stop across the road and a short distance to the Dandenong Train Station, this home is ready for you to make it your own.

Description:
Invest Or Nest
Whether you're a first homebuyer looking to get a foot on the property ladder, or an astutue investor looking to extend your current portfolio, you'll find much to love about this light filled property with its own street frontage. Boasting new carpet and fresh painting throughout, the home offers 2 bedrooms-1 bathroom, a generous living room and a sizeable kitchen-dining space. There is also an L-shaped backyard which is a relative blank canvas, allowing you to sculpt it to suit your needs. Extras include gas ducted heating, split system heating and air-conditioning and a single lock up garage. The home takes pride of place in a popular pocket, in close proximity to local buses with rail links, Dandenong Hospital, quality educational facilities, shopping at both the Dandenong Market and Dandednong Plaza and the popular Dandenong Oasis swim centre. The home is move in ready; it just needs you. Inspect now and make ownership a reality.

Description:
Impressive Family Home with Versatile Style
Premium features, flexible living zones and impeccable presentation highlight the appeal of this stylish double-storey home sitting on approximately 480m2 of land. Delivering an exceptional family lifestyle in a popular and family focused neighbourhood. Impressive interior showcases four bedrooms (all with robes) modern master ensuite & main bathroom.
Beautifully appointed, this sensational contemporary residence of land is bathed in natural light, the generous interiors boasts three separate living zones; a formal living room, an open plan kitchen, meals and family area and an enclosed alfresco area outside which your guests will love.
Impressive from every angle this quality home also is packed with features such as down lights, water tank, side gate security, ducted heating, split system air-conditioning and a double remote lock up garage with additional storage space.
Exceptional lifestyle and location this home is located perfectly within close proximity of Dandenong Plaza, local shops and restaurants and an easy commute to work via the Dandenong Bypass.
